# rawAttestationObject

**Instance Property**

A data object that contains the returned attestation.

## Declaration

```swift
var rawAttestationObject: Data? { get }
```

## Discussion

This object contains the public key. If you request it, it also contains the attestation statement. To learn more, see the [https://www.w3.org/TR/webauthn-2/#attestation-object].
